<section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-WEB:95e9a682-d391-4479-af31-6755ccfa0771-3" data-turn-id-container="request-WEB:95e9a682-d391-4479-af31-6755ccfa0771-3" data-testid="conversation-turn-4" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant">
<div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pb-10 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)">
<div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn">
<div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow">
<div class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" dir="auto" tabindex="0" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="c21f911b-1a94-44e8-a0b1-d6384d606a45" data-turn-start-message="true" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5">
<div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden">
<div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling">
<p data-start="1035" data-end="1062">Complete the diagram below.</p>
<p data-start="1064" data-end="1131">Choose <strong data-start="1071" data-end="1097">NO MORE THAN TWO WORDS</strong> from the passage for each answer.</p>
<p data-start="1133" data-end="1188">Write your answers in boxes 36–40 on your answer sheet.</p>
<p><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," width="553" height="505"></p>
<p data-section-id="p6pc6u" data-start="1190" data-end="1237"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Mobility, stability and combating different</strong></span></p>
<p data-section-id="125fvw4" data-start="1238" data-end="1265"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Types of drag resistance</strong></span></p>
<ul data-start="1267" data-end="1566" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="zgeckk" data-start="1267" data-end="1342">
<p>streamlined shape narrowing towards rear to reduce {turbulent} drag</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="goghs5" data-start="1344" data-end="1388">
<p>fins controlling {up-and-down} movement</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qpi709" data-start="1390" data-end="1435">
<p>fins controlling {sideways} movement</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hufkij" data-start="1437" data-end="1493">
<p>fins which are important for {maneuverability} of fish</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rwho0c" data-start="1495" data-end="1566" data-is-last-node="">
<p>Minimal cross-sectional body area: to decrease {form} drag</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>', NULL, 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">36. turbulent — {streamlined shape narrowing towards rear to reduce turbulent drag}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"29\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn E):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"To <strong data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"24\">reduce the turbulent drag</strong> created as water flows around the moving shape, a <strong data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"100\">rounded front end and tapered back end are required</strong>.\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Hình dáng có đầu tròn và thon gọn dần về phía đuôi/phía sau (tapered back end / narrowing towards rear) là thiết kế để giảm thiểu lực cản nhiễu loạn (<strong data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"162\">turbulent</strong> drag).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">37. up-and-down — {fins controlling up-and-down movement}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"33\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn H):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"33,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“...while <strong data-path-to-node=\"33,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"30\">up-and-down motion is controlled by the pectoral and pelvic fins</strong> on the fish’s sides.”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Vây ngực và vây hông nằm ở hai bên sườn cá chịu trách nhiệm điều khiển chuyển động lên và xuống (<strong data-path-to-node=\"33,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"109\">up-and-down</strong> movement).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">38. sideways — {fins controlling sideways movement}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"31\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn H):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"31,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"The vertically oriented <strong data-path-to-node=\"31,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"45\">dorsal and ventral fins</strong> on the back and belly <strong data-path-to-node=\"31,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"91\">control sideways motion</strong>...\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Vây lưng và vây bụng đặt theo chiều dọc giúp kiểm soát các chuyển động nghiêng/chuyển động ngang (<strong data-path-to-node=\"31,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"110\">sideways</strong> movement/motion).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">39. maneuverability — {fins which are important for maneuverability of fish}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"35\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn H):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"35,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“...the style and arrangement of the <strong data-path-to-node=\"35,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"57\">other fins are crucial for maneuverability</strong>.”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Trừ vây đuôi quyết định tốc độ, kiểu dáng và sự sắp xếp của các vây khác đóng vai trò cốt lõi đối với độ linh hoạt luồn lách (<strong data-path-to-node=\"35,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"138\">maneuverability</strong>) của cá.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">40. form — {Minimal cross-sectional body area: to decrease form drag}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"37\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn E):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"37,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"To <strong data-path-to-node=\"37,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"24\">reduce form drag</strong>, the <strong data-path-to-node=\"37,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"46\">cross-sectional area of the body should be minimal</strong>—a pencil shape would be ideal.\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Diện tích mặt cắt cắt ngang cơ thể ở mức tối thiểu (minimal cross-sectional body area) là giải pháp giúp làm giảm lực cản hình dạng (<strong data-path-to-node=\"37,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"145\">form</strong> drag).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}]', 2);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('c22fd633-48a8-4380-9f33-bf3b219618cf', '8aa9aa47-dca7-4a83-af24-7cf4768e4361', 'fillup', 'Questions 1–4', '<div class="quests-inner-desc">
<div class="txt">
<p><em>Complete the table below.</em></p>
<p><em>Write </em><strong><em>ONE WORD ONLY</em></strong><em> for each answer.</em></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> </p>
