<div class="quests-des">
<div class="content-write">
<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><strong>SCHOOL ART COMPETITION</strong></p>
<div class="quill-better-table-wrapper">
<div class="choice-table-wrap">
<table class="quill-better-table choice-table" style="width: 94.674%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; border: 2px solid #000000;" border="1"><colgroup> <col class="ql-align-center" style="width: 19.913%;" width="132"> <col class="ql-align-center" style="width: 32.7358%;" width="217"> <col class="ql-align-center" style="width: 18.5553%;" width="123"> <col class="ql-align-center" style="width: 28.8136%;" width="191"></colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-row="1">
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="4" rowspan="1" data-row="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;" data-row="1" data-cell="1" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="4" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)"><strong>Arrangements for this year</strong></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr data-row="2">
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="2" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="2" data-cell="1" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)"><strong>Age group</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="2" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="2" data-cell="2" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)"><strong>Theme</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="2" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="2" data-cell="3" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)"><strong>Type of art</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="2" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="2" data-cell="4" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)"><strong>Prize</strong></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr data-row="3">
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="3" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="3" data-cell="1" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">Junior students</p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="3" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="3" data-cell="2" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span class="fill-history-correct">{animals}</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="3" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="3" data-cell="3" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">a drawing</p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="3" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="3" data-cell="4" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">{zoo}</p>
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="3" data-cell="4" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">tickets</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr data-row="4">
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="4" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="4" data-cell="1" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">Senior students</p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="4" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="4" data-cell="2" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">the {city}</p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="4" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="4" data-cell="3" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">a photograph</p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000; border-width: 2px;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="4" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="4" data-cell="4" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">a {travel}</p>
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="4" data-cell="4" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">voucher</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>', NULL, 'gap_filling', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<h2 data-path-to-node=\"2\">PART 1</h2>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Hi John.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Hi Wendy, thanks for coming to discuss the school art competition. I know this is your first year organizing it.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Well I’ve got some ideas, but I’d appreciate some help with arrangements.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> OK. We usually divide the competition into age groups. The first age group is junior students.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> I’ll just note that down.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Last year we went with a theme of family. That worked very well.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Yes, something simple is best for young children I think. How about <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"75\">(1) animals</strong></span> this year?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Sounds good.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> And for the type of art, last year children in the junior age group created a drawing. Shall we stick with that?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Yes and for the prize, I heard last year we gave cinema tickets to the winner. Is that right?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Yes but you know, it might be nice to give the winners tickets to the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"77\">(2) zoo</strong></span> this time.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Good idea, okay.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Finally for the senior students, we also have to think of a theme. I’ve got a couple of ideas. One is the future.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Hmm. I’m not quite sure how students might approach that theme. It could be tricky.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Um, my other idea was the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"33\">(3) city</strong></span>. What do you think?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Good. Students could get some really interesting images with that theme. And for the type of art, I think a photograph would work well.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Great idea. And as a prize, one of our sponsors is willing to donate a voucher that the winner can spend on <strong><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\">(4) travel</span></strong>.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Fantastic! They can find inspiration for their next artworks.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"21\">\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Now let’s discuss some further details of the competition.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Sure.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> First of all, the deadline for submitting artwork. We want to award the prizes on May the 25th. Last year we needed a week to judge the winners and finalize arrangements for the awards night. How about if entrants submit their artwork by <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"244\">(5) 18th May</strong></span>?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Sure. I’ll just note that down. Where should they submit their artworks? At the office?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Actually there’s more space at the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"41\">(6) library</strong></span>, so let’s ask students to take their art there.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Okay. In terms of judging the competition, what did you do last year?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> We used an excellent local artist. We should try and use her again this year. Her name is Rebecca Lee.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Okay. Is that L-double-E?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> No it’s <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"14\">(7) L-E-I-G-H</strong></span>.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Right. I guess I should also note down her number so that I can get in contact with her after we finalize the rest of the competition details.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Sure, I’ve got her number here. Are you ready? It’s <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"58\">(8) 04076254633</strong></span>.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Got it. After the judging, where are we going to display the artworks?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> How about we book the Bridge Street Gallery? It’s a beautiful old building.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> It is. So can you go ahead and book it?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Yes. And do you think we should also publish the artworks in the school <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"78\">(9) magazine</strong></span>?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Yes definitely. I think the winning students would be delighted to see that.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Great. Now in terms of the art exhibition of the students’ work, should we make it a morning event and follow it up with a special lunch or afternoon tea for parents?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"39\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> I was thinking a late afternoon event might be better so that parents can attend after work. After the exhibition, we could put on a <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"140\">(10) dinner</strong></span>. What do you think?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"40\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Yes, that could be nice. Now I wanted…</p>"}]', 0);
SET session_replication_role = DEFAULT;
